    <div id="about">
        <h2>About Wayfinder</h2>
        <hr id="about-hr">
        <p id="about-para">I trained as an historian and always emphasized to my students that our lives only made sense
        because of the stories we tell ourselves: about where we have come from and where we are going. As such,
         I created wayfinder because I believe that everyone needs a place to tell their personal stories and that
         using maps to do so is a particularly innovative and powerful way to do so. Because of the technology now
         available to us, the ability to create and share our experiences in such a visually compelling way has become possible.
         Wayfinder is simply a tool to facilitate this process. For more information, contact Ben Piggot at: wbpiggot@gmail.com.
    </div>

</div>
